description: A pair of green-tinged shrubberies stand beside a dark opening in the sheer cliff face in the face of a sheer cliff, almost like squat, silent guards.  High stone walls rise up on either side of the pass, limiting the view to a rectangular patch of star-dotted sky, its bespeckled surface masked by thin, tattered clouds.  The narrow cleft through the mountain continues northward.

title: [Whistler's Pass]
